。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#唔撤就罷<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港四罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#重組警隊 刑事追究 改革監警制度<br />\n#永遠不光顧荃灣北角元朗商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"f3fb94f39664b68e95c276edf954b840172b3793","tid":1491821,"uid":98141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:31:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3e501fe91d1277ae3481884a10dc1226c26d3d1c","tid":1491821,"uid":70201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:32:30.000Z","msg":"Push!<br />\n<br />\n香港人 我地818係過二百萬㗎!<br />\n[非專業(2)] [徇眾要求] 我想用我嘅統計學幫下民陣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1492094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1492094</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0db32a3a755287ef22f121479deaba82eecd2415","tid":1491821,"uid":220690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:32:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ecbf82ad63a3ac962bb2f6bed29383b57808175f","tid":1491821,"uid":304589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:46:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02d9faf97567f655f70a919c477acefb7c012a78","tid":1491821,"uid":304589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:48:53.000Z","msg":"唔入TG 都幫手推丫!!"},{"pid":"65e0c4698ba78a46aa19237f087dc2917573e04c","tid":1491821,"uid":304589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc5897f172e95be2d1404c543bee5dcabc7fc48","tid":1491821,"uid":41957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:55:31.000Z","msg":"涼下冷氣 睇下野<br />\n但係唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a7f07310d07157a2f0d00409e136ac127e5305","tid":1491821,"uid":20497